    "encrypted": "false",
    "long_instructions": "## AI Threat Detection  \r\n\r\nThis chatbot is a cybersecurity expert AI assistant trained to provide security analysis based on different scenarios you give it.\r\n\r\n### Do This:\r\n\r\n1. Choose a card from your Threat Detected! card deck. \r\n2. Ask the chatbot:\r\n   - How did AI detect this threat?\r\n   - What mitigation strategy does AI recommend?\r\n   - How would this threat have been handled without AI?\r\n3. Use your \"Threat Detection Notetaker\" and answer the prompts. \r\n\r\n\r\n::: details [**Not sure what context to add?**]\r\nUse these prompts to guide your discussion with the AI: \r\n- What is the most likely threat in this scenario?\r\n- How would AI respond differently than a human? \r\n- Why might this be hard for AI to detect?\r\n- What is the best way to stop this threat? \r\n- Could AI ever make a mistake here? What would that look like?\r\n:::",
